description: This skill helps to find movie rating. It is straight forward to use this skill with Alexa. You can get movie rating by telling movie name to this skill.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Box Office what's the rating of Titanic
Tell me review of The Avengers
Tell me movie rating of Iron Man
name: BoxOffice
shortDescription: This skill helps to find movie ratings. It tells you rating on a scale of 10. Where 10 is the highest and 0 is the lowest score ratings can have.
